description:
Panorama of Prophecy: Episode 20 | "The Deadly Mark" | Doug Batchelor

Bible Questions:

00:00 - Intro
07:52 - Where was Daniel when the three young men were cast into the furnace?
09:09 - Are we suppose to observe the Lord's Last Supper in remembrance of Christ?
10:31 - What happens if I miss communion? Can I do it at home?
11:30 - Were Tithes a part of the Ceremonial Laws that were nailed to the Cross?
12:52 - Why are you certain that David, Saul, Solomon, and etc... will be in Heaven when they had so many wives and concubines when they knew the Law of God?
14:50 - Do Angels still visit this Earth today? Will God send His Angels to help us in the Last Days?
16:02 - How can I keep my mind focused on Christ while I am reading the Bible?
17:39 - Why can we not pray to the Saints or Mother Mary?
19:29 - What happens to our Guardian Angel when we die? Does that Angel go on another mission?
23:51 - Sermon - "The Deadly Mark"

Do Angels still visit this Earth today? Will God send His Angels to help us in the Last Days?
How can I keep my mind focused on Christ while I am reading the Bible?
Why can we not pray to the Saints or Mother Mary?
What happens to our Guardian Angel when we die? Does that Angel go on another mission?
